                <p style={{ fontFamily:sans, fontSize:14, lineHeight:1.9, color:"#010000", fontWeight:300 }}>The Venture Studio runs every Venture Semester session. Students build their chosen venture — Da Vinci (commercial market) or Medici (community impact) — with direct faculty mentorship. Every session produces a deliverable. The semester culminates in the Shark Tank-inspired Finale before invited investors, founders, executives, and practitioners.</p>
