              <p style={{ fontFamily: lora, fontSize: 15, color: parch, fontWeight: 400, lineHeight: 1.75, marginBottom: 32 }}>The second Summit — a more advanced agenda designed for students who have progressed through the Venture Semester. By April, students have built a venture, completed an externship, and presented their venture work before invited guests and investors. The Summit II agenda reflects that. Executive dinners, final pitch coaching, and a closing networking event with the broader Excalibur network.</p>
