                  <p style={{ fontFamily:"'Lora', Georgia, serif", fontSize:13, color:"#E4D5C1", fontWeight:400, lineHeight:1.9, marginBottom:28 }}>Faculty guide each team through structured milestones. Select ventures may receive additional mentorship, introductions, or strategic support through the Excalibur network where appropriate.</p>
