                      <p style={{ fontFamily:lora, fontSize:15, lineHeight:1.9, color:"#100F0C", fontWeight:400, marginBottom:16 }}>Every session includes live studio time. Students build their chosen venture — Da Vinci (commercial) or Medici (community impact) — with direct faculty coaching in the room. Every session produces a deliverable. Faculty hold every team to a professional benchmark.</p>
