                n:"III",
                label:"Applied Workshop",
                title:"Venture Studio",
                body:"Every Venture Semester session includes live studio workshop time. Students build their chosen venture in teams, Da Vinci or Medici, under direct faculty mentorship, moving from concept to validation, execution, customer discovery, market testing, MVP, customer validation, early traction, first sales and final presentation. Each week moves the venture forward. The semester culminates in the Shark Tank-inspired Finale, where students present before invited investors, founders, executives, and practitioners, industry & community leaders.",
