              <h2 style={{ fontFamily:ag, fontSize:isMobile?52:80, fontWeight:300, color:"#A48D6E", lineHeight:0.95, letterSpacing:"-0.035em", margin:0 }}>Investor Pitch<br/><em style={{ color:"#A48D6E" }}>&amp; Executive Presence</em></h2>
