              <h2 style={{ fontFamily:ag, fontSize:isMobile?40:64, fontWeight:300, color:"#E4D5C1", lineHeight:0.95, letterSpacing:"-0.03em", margin:0 }}>The Startup<br/><em style={{ color:"#A48D6E" }}>Externship</em></h2>
