                <h2 style={{ fontFamily: "Times, serif", fontSize: "clamp(28px,3vw,42px)", fontWeight: 600, color: "#010000", lineHeight: 1.0, marginBottom: 8 }}>Excalibur “Ivy” Portfolio</h2>
